<span id="freeTextContainer15091395951001011253">Elena Ferrante is a pseudonymous Italian novelist. Ferrante&apos;s books, originally published in Italian, have been translated into many languages. Her four-book series of Neapolitan Novels are her most widely known works.</span>
  <span id="freeText15091395951001011253" style="display:none">Elena Ferrante is a pseudonymous Italian novelist. Ferrante's books, originally published in Italian, have been translated into many languages. Her four-book series of Neapolitan Novels are her most widely known works.</span>
